               <head>Akbarnāmah. Vols. 1-2 by Abū al-Faz̤l ibn Mubārak</head>

               <msContents
                  class="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n80002413 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh85064913 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh2008115921 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh2008115920">
                  <summary> The <title>Akbarnāmah</title> by Abū al-Faz̤l ibn Mubārak in two books
                     up to the end of the 46th regnal year. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4-item1">
                     <author key="viaf_5150639">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Abū al-Faz̤l ibn Mubārak,
                           1551–1602</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">أبو الفضل بن مبارك</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20880">Akbarnāmah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">اكبر نامه</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">(preface, f.1v)ذكر بعضى بشارات غيبى واشارات قدسى كه پيش
                        از سعادت ولادت ...</incipit>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">(book 1 part 1, f.5v) الله اكبر اين جه دريافتى است ثرف
                        وشناختى ...</incipit>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">(book 1 part 2, f.201r) سلسله انتظام كارگاه آفرينش كه
                        مظاهر حقيقت ...</incipit>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">(<hi rend="italic">khātimah</hi>, f.392r) المنّة
                        للّه...</incipit>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">(book 2, f.401v) سخن تازه سازم بنام خداى...</incipit>
                     <note>
                        <p>The preface contains a short index of book 1, down to the end of RY 17. </p>
                        <p>Book 1 dated 27 Rabīʿ al‑awwal 1065 (4 Feb 1655) by <persName role="scr"
                              key="">Shāh Muḥammad ibn Fatḥ Muḥammad Lāhūrī</persName>. </p>
                        <p>Book 2 dated 24 Jumādī al‑ākhir 1106 (9 Feb 1695) by <persName role="scr"
                              key="">Muḥammad Quraysh Quraysh</persName>ī. </p>
                        <p>The <hi rend="italic">khātimah</hi> of book 1 and the opening of book 2
                           are repeated between ff. 632v–640v. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>

