                        <p>Nastaʿlīq script in two hands. Book 1: <persName role="scr" key="">Shāh
                              Muḥammad ibn Fatḥ Muḥammad Lāhūrī</persName>; book 2: <persName
                              role="scr" key="">Muḥammad Quraysh Quraysh</persName></p>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote type="headpiece">Illuminated headpieces on ff.1v, 5v, and 401v. </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="border">Polychrome text frames. </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <p>Various marginal variants noted. </p>
                     <p><persName role="fmo" key="viaf_287207857">Richard Johnson</persName>'s
                        diagonal accession statement (f. 1r): <hi rend="italic">jild-i Akbarnāmah-i
                           sarkār Navvāb Ṣāḥib Mumtāz al-Dawlah Mufakhkhar al-Mulk Ḥusām Jang Mistar
                           Richārd Jānsan Ṣāḥib Bahādur dām iqbāluh. </hi></p>
                     <p>Loosely inserted loans slip signed ‘<persName role="oth" key="viaf_42076979"
                           >H. Beveridge</persName>, 26.2.23’. </p>
                  </additions>

                  <bindingDesc>
